<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT62">
<l>tiruṉiṉṟa pakkan tiṟaviteṉ ṟōrār</l>
<l>karuṉiṉṟa kallārk kuraippar tiruvirunta</l>
<l>mārpaṉ cirītaraṉṟaṉ vaṇṭulavu taṇṭuḻāy</l>
<l>tārtaṉṉaic cūṭit tarittu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who—[not] having adorned themselves with and borne</l>
<l>the garland of cool tulasi swarmed by bees, of Śrīdhara, on whose chest Śrī stays—</l>
<l>do not know that the side where Śrī stays is the Cause [of the world],</l>
<l>Will proclaim those [gods that] stayed in wombs [as being the Cause] to the ignorant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
